- Prioritize "Mobile-First" design using clean CSS.
- Use Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+). Avoid external frameworks unless requested.
- Maintain PWA compatibility (manifest.json, Service Worker).
- When writing code, prioritize performance and fast load times.
- If writing Spanish UI, ensure the code remains consistent with the structure.
- Always provide concise, readable code.
- If the user asks for new features, ensure they respect the existing SPA (Single Page Application) navigation logic.